<bug>
	<id>15146</id>
	<title>One invalid id makes the whole ?ids=.._.._.. request fail</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">When you request invalid id_ like
https://graph.facebook.com/434085561047?access_token=...
you get the  invalid id  error.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">It s ok.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.3">But in case of multiple ids_ like in
https://graph.facebook.com/?ids=4_434085561047&amp;access_token=...
the same error is return for the request as a whole_ even if id 4 is correct.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">This pretty invalidates ?</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.2">ids=.... style requests.</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.3">errors (at least this one) should be returns per id in the result.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
